history.content:
Hello Everyone!

Are you looking for teammates or co-founders? Do you want to explore real entrepreneurship and use your expertise? Partnering with Berkeley Entrepreneurs Association (BEA), Bridge97 is helping you find your co-founders or create your interest project team in the UC Berkeley community.

Connect now: https://bridge97-lp.webflow.io/

About Bridge97

Bridge97 honors the tradition when the 97th chemical element, Berkelium, was discovered at Berkeley via high-energy particles colliding. It aims to build bridges between founders and spark innovation via high-energy idea collision.
history.subject: Looking for co-founders or cool startup projects? Let BEA x Bridge97 help you!
